    "description": "IMV Corporation manufactures and sells vibration simulation systems and measuring systems in Japan, Asia, Europe, the United States of America, and internationally. The company offers vibration simulation systems; test and solution services; and measuring devices, such as vibration measuring and monitoring devices, earthquake monitoring devices, and environmental reliability evaluation systems. It also offers quality control services to automobiles, aerospace, defense, and electronics industries. In addition, it provides vibration controllers; rental vibration testing machine; seismometers; vibration pick-up and sensors; and insulation degradation evaluation test equipment. It also develops, produces, repairs, and maintains vibration and environmental test systems. In addition, it offers test house, measuring analysis, and other consulting services for vibration tests. Further, the company leases vibration test machine. IMV Corporation was incorporated in 1957 and is headquartered in Osaka, Japan."
